<domains>
- "symptoms": Physical or mental health conditions and clinical signs (e.g., headache, fever, cough, nausea, toothache).
- "diets": Nutrition, therapeutic eating plans, and weight management advice (e.g., diabetes diet, cholesterol, caloric intake).
- "hot_topics": Trending health news, public health alerts, and time-sensitive events (e.g., Covid-19, vaccination updates, pandemics).
- "service_desk": Technical support and critical escalations for emergencies requiring immediate attention (e.g., Emergency SOS, technician needed).
- "contacts": Facility locations, administrative contact details, and booking channels (e.g., hospital address, phone numbers).
- "medical_package": Structured preventative screening sets and wellness checkup bundles (e.g., senior/adolescent screening, package details).
- "billing": Financial inquiries, including insurance procedures, service costs, and payments (e.g., pricing, fees, consultation rates).
- "general": Broad wellness tips, healthy lifestyle advice, and any medical topics not covered above (e.g., generic health tips).
</domains>

